6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to schools; amending Section 1,
Chapter 289, O.S.L. 2023, as last amended by Section
8 2, Chapter 480, O.S.L. 2025 (70 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 18-114.15), which relates to minimum salary
9 and benefits; requiring certified personnel to
receive a salary increase in certain instances;
10 providing an effective date; and declaring an
emergency.
11
