16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 289, O.S.L.
18 2023, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 480, O.S.L. 2025 (70
19 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 18-114.15), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 18-114.15. A. Beginning with the 2025-2026 school
21 year, certified personnel, as defined in Section 26-103 of this
22 title, in the public schools of this state shall receive in salary
23 and/or fringe benefits not less than the amounts specified in the
24 following schedule:
